{"tid":644124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 先達店疑晒「黃牛磚」　 子華fans圍剿籲罷買","createTime":"2018-04-27T04:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7ee7935a7542ea4c52bd1164968c7f3b56c565","tid":644124,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180427/20374443?_ga=2.136562736.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F20374443%3F_ga%3D2.136562736.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=ZbLDp%2FSOqoVC0pFaSHQ%2Fr5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=85ddf292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F20374443%3F_ga%3D2.136562736.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=a4b28476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180427/20374443?_ga=2.136562736.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n先達店疑晒「黃牛磚」　<br />\n子華fans圍剿籲罷買<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180427/large/a2103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180427%2Flarge%2Fa2103a.gif&h=4ac696c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■就係呢6磚子華棟篤笑門票挑起一場腥風血雨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先達手機店「轉型」炒黃牛飛？黃子華宣佈棟篤笑加場，15萬張公開發售門票日前依然係一天沽清，唔少擁躉仲係未買到飛，苦不堪言。就喺呢個時候，有人爆料先達一間樓上手機店前晚突然喺fb貼出相片，相中可見6大叠「磚頭飛」，估計當中有超過200張黃子華棟篤笑門票，個post仲笑言話相中嘅票係「今日戰績」，即時畀網民話佢哋係炒黃牛飛，紛紛留言聲討，同時亦激嬲咗大批子華fans。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180427/large/a2103b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180427%2Flarge%2Fa2103b.gif&h=c4499125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店員稱轉貼自fb<br />\n<br />\n該6叠黃子華棟篤笑門票，日期分別係7月6、21、27同28號，雖然有小量網民即時留言問門票「幾錢？」，但更多網民留言鬧爆嗰間手機店係「集團式黃牛黨」，有人怒斥「今次關公都幫你唔到」，亦都有子華擁躉留言引述黃子華早前為打擊黃牛當做嘅公開呼籲：「寧願個位吉，都唔好益黃牛！」不少網民都話，先達手機舖平時炒貴晒啲iPhone圖利已經乞人憎，𠵱家竟然撈埋炒門票，覺得忍無可忍，一時間群情洶湧，至前晚10點幾，該手機店已經將「今日戰績」張相刪除，但仍難息眾怒，店方fb續有人留言辱罵。<br />\n<br />\n記者噚日傍晚到先達了解，發現該樓上手機店仲照常營業，記者問店員施先生有冇賣子華門票時，佢就有啲無奈，解釋話喎：「我只係見到網上有張咁嘅（大叠門票）相，於是轉貼上fb箒&hellip;&hellip;講笑咋，我真係冇賣（黃牛）賣㗎。」佢又話喺網上點解釋都冇用，所以最後決定刪咗張相。記者就發現無論大家信唔信佢嘅解釋，黃牛票問題始終未解決，噚日繼續有開價1.5萬元黃牛飛，睇嚟要修例先有機會杜絕到黃牛黨。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 深水埗石壆現睡羅漢"},{"pid":"ec6031e3dbdae2c44ce09c400e1c1112c7d492c5","tid":644124,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"唯有睇dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0f7e9bd62c4bf785a9a601dd45aa25a4cad38e","tid":644124,"uid":167573,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"我就不信了<br />\n<br />\n係人都知， 依家先達d舖頭都開始轉型。 靠iphone都搵唔到錢.<br />\n<br />\n所以gay lo 都賣下牙刷鬚刨<br />\n<br />\n好多鋪頭都轉賣iqos.<br />\n<br />\n所以炒演唱會係絕對有可能嘅事"},{"pid":"4aefe9ed4b4f0a8e95bc33f3f10d8f8ae0ac8adc","tid":644124,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/140209_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F140209_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=912d37fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9d3536a656ab369fee9d60fcc3c2c27eedce4f8","tid":644124,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n成個場都ON撚99<br />\n全場都不務正業咁濟<br />\n一味識炒賣投機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ec987da5e54f4ee56148e6b4cdfed2261a2e9d","tid":644124,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9d3536a656ab369fee9d60fcc3c2c27eedce4f8","tid":644124,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n成個場都ON撚99<br />\n全場都不務正業咁濟<br />\n一味識炒賣投機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"成個支那同香港都係咁,所以美國是但bam你一樣嘢都等收皮"},{"pid":"0d50218435582a08dde89a49b6e9b01d47e99d12","tid":644124,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母<br />\n成個場都ON撚99<br />\n全場都不務正業咁濟<br />\n一味識炒賣投機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先達的正業就係炒iphone 者。<br />\n仲有咩正業？"},{"pid":"07aa9081352614b5819992a6c214946c3cbe4977","tid":644124,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"認真一問，呢張相唔係早幾日個post，有條友話&ldquo;香港人唔珍惜黃牛&ldquo;嗰張相黎㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5290bddab7bc891b72bc531195f84afe2c50372d","tid":644124,"uid":63017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"叫子華取消面個兩張飛佢啦"},{"pid":"53f10f1064023967e9f924b1b430b1cc99f948ed","tid":644124,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"應該有賣飛員工內部流出"}]}